{"tid":2492907,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日女中學生被覇凌 屍體雪溶後被發現","createTime":"2021-04-17T12:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:38:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":19,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0c79e71fada192205c2a4a002c32853e6166d4","tid":2492907,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/jn2p6vD.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fjn2p6vD.jpeg&h=de05e4d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n春天到來還很久的3月下旬，北海道旭川住宅區還積有近一公尺的雪，在漸漸<br />\n融雪的公園一角，住在旭川的14歲女中<br />\n學生廣瀨爽彩冰冷的屍體在雪中冒出頭來<br />\n<br />\n廣瀨爽彩在今年2月13傍晚6點多出門後<br />\n就此失蹤，家人朋友及志工幫忙找人，但<br />\n再也不見其行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n這個月天氣暖和後，雪開始融化，<br />\n部分屍體顯露出來，附近居民發現後<br />\n趕緊報警，警方到場把屍體挖堀出來<br />\n，爽彩已成為一具冰凍的屍身，身上<br />\n僅著清薄衣物， 判斷死因為低溫症。<br />\n<br />\n爽彩的母親向文春週刊揭露此事， 爽彩<br />\n在學被複數男學生學長性虐待及覇凌，且<br />\n有不當的影片被上傳網路，但這事卻被<br />\n學校掩蓋，導致爽彩自殺，但自殺未遂。<br />\n<br />\n學校隱暱此事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/10ivnmq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2F10ivnmq&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=34faf239\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/10ivnmq</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/7z23kef3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2F7z23kef3&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=0948bc7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/7z23kef3</a>"},{"pid":"09909e273c68bc1d9bd8b24f7d14ef4e5fd1280b","tid":2492907,"uid":167464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"啲㗎仔都幾撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891082dfd57b02e61bfe761d16e608027e995880","tid":2492907,"uid":49004,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"世界冇報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"