公園裡玩耍的小學生，不少人圍著爽彩。女生們叫爽彩像早前發裸照一樣現場做做看，還要求她當場自慰。爽彩被帶到小學的殘廁，逃不掉也求助不了，只能聽從他們的話。自此爽彩便自暴自棄，連抵抗也放棄了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>走頭無路 欺凌煽動跳進河中</strong><br />\n6月22日，欺凌者10人迫爽彩從4米高的河堤跳進河中。雖然此事有被當地新聞記載，當中卻有不少描述是不正確的。據母親指當天下著雨，欺凌者共10人之多，其中一人笑著說「我會把一直以來的事說給不知情的人聽的，照片也會讓全校更多人知道」爽彩馬上請求「不要這樣做」卻被說「去死」。<br />\n<br />\n「好的。我會去死的所以請把照片刪掉吧。」爽彩回答道。然而其他人更是煽動她「連死的勇氣也沒有說什麼想死」。結果爽彩一手跨過柵欄，跳進河中。說是自殺未遂，倒不如說是為了逃離欺凌者只好跳進河更為正確。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/asahikawa-icing-incident/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fasahikawa-icing-incident%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=90e8c923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/asahikawa-icing-incident/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 早知唔睇<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"ca1f737078a05bf625c99f0b723f3ab53d7a3aa9","tid":2492907,"uid":16123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"但係未成年好似冇咩事<br />\n求個十條友結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eefb5619bd058b0a80db47af5f0470b3de68d08","tid":2492907,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"所羅門的偽證？"},{"pid":"86417086d20004196fd3d4262110d2f0334771cf","tid":2492907,"uid":202125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89cb17ffd338828a509443f6661c0ccb8ef63fde","tid":2492907,"uid":2914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"搵人起底捉個班男仔去打去姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老味咁叫欺凌?